/public/docs/attribute/flight

Format: (Living_Object)->set_attribute("flight", iValue);

Description:
  Flight will allow the Living_Object to fly in the skies of DarkWind.
  A value of 1 is standard, and allows flight, and combat will make
  them land. A value of 2 or more will cause the Living_Object to
  not land from combat. Those with a value of 2 or more will have to
  manually be forced to land and the attribute cleared.
